## What aipedia.wiki Is

aipedia.wiki is an independent, editorially-managed encyclopedia of AI tools. Every tool on this site has been reviewed, scored, and verified by our editorial team. We don't accept sponsored placements, "featured" tiers, or paid rankings of any kind.

Most AI tool directories list thousands of products with one-line descriptions. We do the opposite — deep, honest reviews of the tools that matter, written as reference pages that stay current.

**Current coverage:**
- **{allTools.length} tool reviews** across {allCategories.length} categories
- **{allComparisons.length} head-to-head comparisons**
- **{allUseCases.length} use-case guides** (best-of lists, workflow stacks, alternatives)
- **{allDead.length} archived dead tools** — because knowing what failed matters

